➜Migratory birds protection in China
http://www.sohu.com/a/437672672_162758	38860
<p align="justify">Autumn and winter are the seasons for the large-scale southward migration of migratory birds in China. At present, migratory birds protection activites initiated by volunteers from all over the country have been vigorously carried out. As the activities drew more and more public participation, they have become an important force in the construction of ecological civilization and the protection of wild animals and plants. </p>
